{"tid":1842565,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"醫護界咁多位 可唔可以放低包袱一次","createTime":"2020-01-25T18:19:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T14:42:57.000Z","uid":125366,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b0e9583e60625e54c81e3e37125e45663369a390","tid":1842565,"uid":125366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T18:19:31.000Z","msg":"三罷嗰時其實都有人講過<br />\n罷工係最低成本嘅行動<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">人愈多 就愈低成本</span><br />\n有啲人要養家 供樓<br />\n但罷得工嘅唔係個個都無包袱<br />\n某啲人想無後果咁罷工 <br />\n首先你要放低自己嘅包袱<br />\n人夠多 自然就無後果<br />\n<br />\n為一班毫無防護意識 周圍散播病菌嘅大陸人賣命 請問你甘唔甘心<br />\n或者你會覺得醫護無得揀救咩人 有人就要去救<br />\n但而家個重點係 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">政府唔封關 用所謂嘅人道理由等疫症繼續蔓延 再叫班前線執手尾</span><br />\n係政府無做野去阻止病菌散播<br />\n所謂嘅措施有無效 大家都有目共睹<br />\n<br />\n而家講緊嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">唔係你有無道德 而係政府辦事不力</span><br />\n仲要好似驚疫情唔夠勁 幫手助攻埋<br />\n<br />\n有醫德 有責任感嘅你 覺得繼續返工救人係無錯<br />\n相信好多香港人一樣會支持<br />\n但唔等於你要為呢個無良政府執爛攤子<br />\n政府做得唔好你唔出聲 自己硬食<br />\n佢自然唔覺得有問題 <br />\n然後下次又會繼續係咁<br />\n你又可以幫佢頂到幾多次？<br />\n<br />\n無人想俾人秋後算帳<br />\n所果如果大家都願意放低包袱 響應罷工<br />\n到時個包袱就唔係包袱<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 會罷<br />\n<br />\n香港人請好好保重身體 場仗仲要打好耐<br />\n香港人加油！"},{"pid":"aee4d7d5d1f08d6c36d4fbc68f4f775c48e22ddd","tid":1842565,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T18:50:42.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />罷工救港 功德無量<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請加入工會</div>"},{"pid":"137eb226f09ec663c84a41373c2934d510fdbbe7","tid":1842565,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T18:51:08.000Z","msg":"入去推一推<br />\n<br />\n請不要再說：「我支持醫護罷工。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1842379\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1842379</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f29e6b8c68a755559aaaacfd10d72c89cf6297e6","tid":1842565,"uid":64126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T19:19:56.000Z","msg":"多謝你<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">罷工唔止係醫護人員嘅責任<br />\n<br />\n係全香港700萬市民嘅責任<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全港三罷 刻不容緩</span><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oisbVO4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoisbVO4.jpg&h=e95b4412&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">唔罷 下一個中招嘅好可能係你</div>"},{"pid":"86b937fe10b046ac6fbed36b192eb195002900ea","tid":1842565,"uid":64126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T19:20:28.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4946703cd280a19b0ccf26bc891d059a87df68d6","tid":1842565,"uid":125366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:42:57.000Z","msg":"2月3"}]}